room_title: Escape room "Escape from the Black and White" by Amaze Room Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
room_address: 3209 Gresham Lake Rd. Suite 128 Raleigh, NC 27615
room_description:
Simon's life as he knew it vanished in an instant. As a world-famous pianist, he is now plagued with partial amnesia. You, as Simon, only have a faint lingering memory of the black and white piano keys that brought you to discover the woman of your dreams.
You have 60 minutes to attempt to retrace history and fill in the missing pieces. Now, who is she...?
